    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make your own way through the wilderness: build a cozy cabin or take your tent to discover more. Retro vibes and evergreen optimism ensoul this survival adventure featuring clever craftables, curious critters, and a handful of inspiring landmarks tucked away throughout.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693410/extras/35728d87425e78d6208bf8b96065faeb.poster.avif?t=1768954027\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693410/extras/35728d87425e78d6208bf8b96065faeb.webm?t=1768954027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693410/extras/35728d87425e78d6208bf8b96065faeb.mp4?t=1768954027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survival Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search the world for resources and craft new items to help aid in your survival. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693410/extras/63417c4cc05ad2ea3980962f7add8a7b.poster.avif?t=1768954027\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693410/extras/63417c4cc05ad2ea3980962f7add8a7b.webm?t=1768954027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693410/extras/63417c4cc05ad2ea3980962f7add8a7b.mp4?t=1768954027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Frontier Living</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cultivate your frontier home base by building advanced structures like the cache. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693410/extras/f9468db9445e8156eb0c8f827b741603.poster.avif?t=1768954027\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693410/extras/f9468db9445e8156eb0c8f827b741603.webm?t=1768954027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693410/extras/f9468db9445e8156eb0c8f827b741603.mp4?t=1768954027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >World Exploration</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your tent to camp anywhere in the world, allowing you to hike to new locations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693410/extras/582e83270706d03a0e61cacfadd3f4f0.poster.avif?t=1768954027\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693410/extras/582e83270706d03a0e61cacfadd3f4f0.webm?t=1768954027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693410/extras/582e83270706d03a0e61cacfadd3f4f0.mp4?t=1768954027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Inspiring Landmarks</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful waterfalls, mysterious mines and more will break up the survival gameplay, allowing you to reflect on your time in the wild.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693410/extras/da9579fbdb037b3e80241b87d1f4a38b.poster.avif?t=1768954027\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693410/extras/da9579fbdb037b3e80241b87d1f4a38b.webm?t=1768954027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693410/extras/da9579fbdb037b3e80241b87d1f4a38b.mp4?t=1768954027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And More!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We'll be continuing to update this <strong>About</strong> section as we build out the features in <i>On My Own: New Frontier</i>, so be sure to <strong><u>Wishlist &amp; Follow</u></strong> for the latest news updates.</p>",
